    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "Hi @oliverbeck-dev, InstantSearch still doesn't support on-demand update. For now [Haroen's suggestion](https://github.com/algolia/instantsearch/issues/5252#issuecomment-1363060527) is the way to go. You can get more information on `:on-state-change` for Vue InstantSearch [in the API reference](https://www.algolia.com/doc/api-reference/widgets/instantsearch/vue/#widget-param-on-state-change).",
